Pillars
--------------
Pillar is just simple data. To create/setup pillars is exactly same as states.
If you have already gone throught the previous tutorials on salt-states then pillar will be very easy.


Read this article completely:
http://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/topics/pillar/

Read this skipping the last python part:
http://dev.mlsdigital.net/posts/SaltStackBeyondJinjaStates/



Macro/function using in salt/ jinja renderer
http://docs.saltstack.com/en/latest/ref/renderers/all/salt.renderers.jinja.html




